 hints on the\nintrinsic nature of suspended nanowire and can be interesting for in the field\nof spintronics as well as for the manipulation of Majorana bound states in\ndevices based on hybrid semiconductors.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Wed, 11 Jul 2018 20:32:50 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Thu, 15 Nov 2018 08:10:15 GMT"}],"update_date":"2019-02-14"}
