GeV,\nwhich explains the guessed choice of $2-3$ GeV using conventional\nscale-setting. The scale-fixed $e^+ e^- \\to J/\\psi+\\eta_c$ cross-section\npredicted by the PMC shows excellent agreement with the Belle and Babar\nmeasurements, emphasizing the importance of a rigorous renormalization\nscale-setting procedure.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jul 2018 09:59:41 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 16 Oct 2018 11:10:35 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-11-07"}
