results is\nGabriel-Roiter (co)measure, an invariant assigned to modules of finite length,\nand defined by Gabriel and Ringel. This, in fact, provides an application of\nthe Gabriel-Roiter (co)measure in the category of maximal Cohen-Macaulay\nmodules.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jul 2018 10:12:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-13"}
