eds and constraints. We discuss our and our students' experiences when\nemploying the proposed methodology to 4th generation (4G) long-term-evolution\n(LTE) standard education at Barcelona Tech.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Thu, 12 Jul 2018 06:38:58 GMT"}],"update_date":"2018-07-17"}
